snippet.title: Space Entity
snippet.description:
Space Entity is a 1-4 player online co-op survival horror game. A entity is within the space ship. Get the power back on and use the escape pods to live on. Coming on Steam

Follow development through the socials below.

Discord - https://discord.gg/ZeyjRuBrRB
Twitch - https://www.twitch.tv/surprisedhotdoglimited
Kick - https://kick.com/surprisedhotdogs
Steam - https://store.steampowered.com/app/2276880/Space_Entity/
